00:14:51.875 --> 00:14:53.466
Fuyutsuki-sensei!

00:14:53.642 --> 00:14:55.370
Fuyutsuki!

00:14:55.910 --> 00:14:59.866
Fuyutsuki, Fuyutsuki.
I'm so glad you're safe.

00:15:00.011 --> 00:15:02.876
Don't be stupid.
Do you understand?

00:15:05.547 --> 00:15:07.706
