I can't say no to her.

00:16:18.709 --> 00:16:22.608
If you run to Hakuba
every time you go nuts at school...

00:16:22.676 --> 00:16:25.200
...the commute will break you.

00:16:25.277 --> 00:16:28.972
What does this place mean to you?

00:16:29.646 --> 00:16:34.945
This is where I made my decision
to be a teacher.

00:16:35.681 --> 00:16:38.648
I was working at this B&amp;B
during the summer...

00:16:38.716 --> 00:16:40.410
...while I was in college.

00:16:40.617 --> 00:16:43.709
The girl you met was Hitomi.

00:16:44.085 --> 00:16:46.881
The owner's daughter, right?

00:16:47.286 --> 00:16:49.116
How did you know?

00:16:49.354 --> 00:16:52.843
Her letters.
They were all over your desk.

00:16:52.921 --> 00:16:53.910
What?

00:16:54.022 --> 00:16:57.887
