hobby and favorite TV star.

00:18:12.186 --> 00:18:17.552
I tried to understand them.
I don't know what to do anymore.

00:18:18.087 --> 00:18:22.111
I don't know. I've never put
that much thought into it.

00:18:22.222 --> 00:18:25.678
I envy you, Onizuka.
You have no worries.

00:18:26.024 --> 00:18:28.957
Oh, I have many worries.

00:18:29.125 --> 00:18:32.854
Like having only 50 yen left
before payday.

00:18:32.927 --> 00:18:35.587
That's not what you meant?

00:18:35.894 --> 00:18:39.453
I was hoping I would feel better
if I saw Hitomi.

00:18:39.696 --> 00:18:41.958
But something is wrong.

00:18:42.096 --> 00:18:46.792
