from the past are falling apart.

00:18:55.335 --> 00:18:57.427
Okay. Let me talk to her.

00:18:57.802 --> 00:18:58.769
What?

00:18:58.837 --> 00:19:00.098
Count on me.

00:19:00.170 --> 00:19:01.363
Wait, Onizuka!

00:19:01.771 --> 00:19:04.260
Where is your daughter?

00:19:05.105 --> 00:19:08.436
I think she's at our main house.

00:19:09.106 --> 00:19:10.539
Onizuka!

00:19:10.640 --> 00:19:12.232
What's next?

00:19:21.712 --> 00:19:24.975
Hey, are you the brat
who doesn't like teachers?

00:19:25.047 --> 00:19:26.604
Could you tell me who you are?

00:19:26.681 --> 00:19:30.842
Eikichi Onizuka, 22 years old.
I am the greatest teacher in Japan!

00:19:31.015 --> 00:19:32.709
Onizuka! Stop it.

00:19:33.316 --> 00:19:35.647
Are you also a teacher?

00:19:35.817 --> 00:19:38.215
Get out of my house.
I don't want to talk to any teachers.

00:19:38.284 --> 00:19:39.615
- Hitomi.
- Go home!

00:19:39.686 --> 00:19:41.549
No, I won't.

00:19:41.619 --> 00:19:43.279
Why don't you like teachers?

00:19:43.653 --> 00:19:45.279
Tell me why!

00:19:48.055 --> 00:19:50.147
Sure. I'll tell you why.

00:19:50.223 --> 00:19:53.122
We were abandoned
by Sagara-sensei.

00:19:53.290 --> 00:19:54.586
What?

00:19:54.657 --> 00:19:57.681
She was having an affair
with another teacher.

00:19:57.758 --> 00:19:58.952
Affair?

00:19:59.060 --> 00:20:01.117
- Are you kidding?
- No.

00:20:01.527 --> 00:20:04.494
She did something
she shouldn't have done.

00:20:04.795 --> 00:20:07.160
You call yourself a teacher?

00:20:07.762 --> 00:20:11.662
How could you make us
support your affair...

00:20:11.764 --> 00:20:14.492
...with a married man in this school?

00:20:15.699 --> 00:20:18.825
Are you saying
a teacher can't be in love?

00:20:19.434 --> 00:20:22.026
Are you going to justify
what you did?

00:20:22.502 --> 00:20:24.833
What are you going to tell the kids?

00:20:25.236 --> 00:20:28.170
I have no intention
of making any excuses.

00:20:28.238 --> 00:20:30.864
I'll just tell them the facts
as they are.

00:20:30.938 --> 00:20:32.529
What were you thinking?

00:20:32.639 --> 00:20:35.800
Principal, fire her now!

00:20:36.607 --> 00:20:38.403
So Sagara-sensei was...

00:20:38.508 --> 00:20:41.873
We were her last students
before the school closed.

00:20:41.942 --> 00:20:44.807
She quit teaching school
before we graduated.

00:20:44.877 --> 00:20:47.003
She must have gone
somewhere with him.

00:20:47.111 --> 00:20:49.305
She's that kind of person.

00:20:49.712 --> 00:20:52.873
Tomorrow the school will be gone.
Demolished.

00:20:52.946 --> 00:20:54.708
What do you mean?

00:20:54.780 --> 00:20:57.304
The school will be blown up
for a film.

00:20:57.382 --> 00:20:58.939
That'll give me a break.

00:20:59.749 --> 00:21:01.875
Stupid.

00:21:02.317 --> 00:21:06.341
Don't pout over such a thing.
A teacher is human, too.

00:21:06.418 --> 00:21:09.442
There's nothing wrong
with her loving someone.

00:21:09.520 --> 00:21:10.487
Onizuka!

00:21:10.554 --> 00:21:13.783
Don't talk like that
without thinking of her feelings.

00:21:13.854 --> 00:21:15.753
Her feelings?

00:21:16.155 --> 00:21:19.611
How about his wife's, child's,
and our feelings?!

00:21:19.690 --> 00:21:22.248
She is the one who doesn't care
about people's feelings!

00:21:22.391 --> 00:21:24.654
She's just selfish.

00:21:25.158 --> 00:21:31.290
That's why!
That's why I hate teachers!

00:21:48.170 --> 00:21:52.903
Subete no hito wo aiseru wake ja

00:21:53.075 --> 00:21:56.135
nainara semete aisuru hito wo

00:21:56.412 --> 00:22:00.314
Uragi razu ni utagawazu ni

00:22:00.482 --> 00:22:05.715
semetari nikundari shinai de

00:22:06.689 --> 00:22:10.284
Mujaki de irukoto ga

00:22:10.559 --> 00:22:14.495
hito wo kizutsukete shimau no?

00:22:14.763 --> 00:22:22.636
Shizuka na jounetsu ga
hitomi no oku de sawagi dasu...

00:22:22.905 --> 00:22:27.433
Anata ni meguri aete

00:22:29.178 --> 00:22:32.705
Hateshinai toki no naka de

00:22:32.948 --> 00:22:36.941
jibun ni nani ga dekiru

00:22:37.186 --> 00:22:40.986
Ima wa mada chiisaku temo

00:22:41.190 --> 00:22:45.149
kagayaki keseya shinai yo

00:22:45.394 --> 00:22:48.989
Kobore souna namida no tsubu

00:22:49.331 --> 00:22:53.267
nagasazu mune ni tamete

00:22:53.535 --> 00:22:57.130
Isshun wo tsuyoku iki yo

00:22:57.339 --> 00:23:03.278
ichizu na shizuku ni natte

00:23:16.792 --> 00:23:18.589
NEXT EPISODE

00:23:21.530 --> 00:23:23.828
The demolition is going to start.

00:23:26.468 --> 00:23:30.404
If not blown to pieces,
then vaporized.

00:23:33.075 --> 00:23:34.440
The other end!

00:23:36.178 --> 00:23:37.611
Wait for me.